attributes.Long form description: The student changes the battery and the SD card of the GoPro.The student turns the GoPro on and off; after that, the student assembles the strap and then changes it to the tripod. The student changes the tripod to the handheld grip. In the end, the student disassembles the handheld grip.

attributes.Transcription: Hello and thank you for going to take part in our study.In front of you, you will see a GoPro action camera. We will be using it for this task.
First, can you please change the battery in the camera?

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the battery of the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the micro SD card in the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the SD card of the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Next, Please turn on the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student turns the GoPro on.
The student turns the GoPro off.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please turn off the camera.
Next, please mount the shoulder strap to the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student mounts the strap to the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the mount from the shoulder strap to the tripod.

attributes.Action sentence: The student replaces the strap with the tripod.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please change the mount from the tripod to the handheld mode.

attributes.Action sentence: The student exchanges the tripod for the handheld grip.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student tries to assembles the handheld grip in a wrong way.
The student tries to assembles the handheld grip in a wrong way.

attributes.Transcription: Next, please disconnect the mount of the camera.

attributes.Action sentence: The student disassembles the handheld grip of the GoPro.

attributes.Transcription: Let's put everything for this task, you may now press the stop button.
